com.apriori.vars

Class VariableLong

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • com.apriori.vars.VariableLong
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class VariableLong
extends Number
implements Cloneable
    A simple variable reference for a long. This is the primitive specialization of Variable for long.

    This class provides nearly the same API as AtomicLong. However, this version is not thread-safe. If the variable is being accessed from multiple threads, use an AtomicLong instead.
